Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  是岩城兄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊  我最近搞到个厉害玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱我还有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上着  我当然在上课
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.32,0:02:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（老妈只会唠叨气死了）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看这间公寓  在泡沫经济后就被废弃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,业主也不知去向  从此无人问津
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚突然倒塌...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打电话的是你妈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么事  只是照惯例打来问问而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:03:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外离它二百米远的一座楼房的屋顶...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（昨晚到底算什么）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（本来够进入气氛的了）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.38,0:03:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（结果我只是电灯泡）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.91,0:03:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（她心里面只有加藤）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（气死人）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本台刚刚收到的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘消失的看露毛写真集的\N高中生的追踪采访
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（还没结束吗）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.32,0:03:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续为您播出最新消息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（而且都开始用\N“看露毛写真集的高中生”来称呼了）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是玄野君吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然加藤君才不会看那些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么能确定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.98,0:03:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是说带着弟弟寄住在亲戚那吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.11,0:03:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定不会看的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（越来越向着加藤了）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤君真辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:04:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家要照顾弟弟\N到了那房间要照顾大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说他很善良吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就这样婆婆妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么说话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有加藤君还不知会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是会开枪的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.35,0:04:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去一次就会清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那种情况下  光是善良是活不下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.15,0:04:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管加藤怎么强调要大家一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我也这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真心话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（到底在想什么）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回不能轻饶你这小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.22,0:05:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃什么早饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天又穿着满是泥的鞋进家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.91,0:05:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把地上弄得全是泥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小步  小步  他怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屁用没有的东西  还一个劲要早饭吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗  不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的不对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是说话呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里没有给你们吃的饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小步吃掉的份我买回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.05,0:05:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想顶嘴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还敢反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为自己是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那什么眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我住手  你再打小步的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再打他的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再打他  我不知道会干出什么来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.11,0:06:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事了  求求你别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个都赶快给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会走的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AC如果等于1
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BC就等于根号3
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（岸本？）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤君努力想让每一个人都活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.25,0:07:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对别人的生命象自己的一样珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（怎么又来了）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又善良又强悍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是和他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再没有那样的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（说什么啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（别用那么性感的样子说这话）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...180度老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野他又“立起来”了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.75,0:07:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野同学你又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又出去追那偷书的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:08:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他偷了书就这样掖着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  您要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前不久定的书到了没？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的姓名？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱丘  樱丘圣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多好听的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么写的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了是《米兰达·福斯特的迷》吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思还没到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.98,0:08:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这书没有再版  实在很难
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最近还进书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.48,0:08:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀呀  下星期晚些天也许会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一进到了会给您打电话的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是玩具枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从哪搞来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就有点不好开口了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好开口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  这种玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个月的钱用这个抵行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你他妈说真的？我要这烂东西干么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你拿钱来的  拿钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拿钱出来听到没
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到你姥姥那儿拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用不着什么钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你马上就要见阎王了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是最强的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.71,0:10:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬那么高是很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.52,0:10:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了小朋友该回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直把打工挣的钱存着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是我们的新家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  小步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.75,0:10:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.85,0:10:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能早点存够钱搬出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  今后不用再受气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.75,0:11:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的...很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起加油吧  哥哥  我很快也能干活了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行你要上学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被褥怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.05,0:11:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友把用过的给我了  我得去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去  一个人拿太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用  小步你在家看电视吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.05,0:11:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到放动画的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.11,0:11:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以看电视？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.52,0:11:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天起天天都能看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给刚才拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能做些简单的饭菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是叫连锁店的饭太花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了花不了多少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我们这不算是同居吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天开始做饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你生什么气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.01,0:11:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没生气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可玄野君你就生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（你跟加藤就从不顶嘴）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  还在这
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就会赚大钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要搬到更大的房子去住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有那么多钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.28,0:12:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明没有奶水  喂什么喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.91,0:12:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪只顾买烟忘记买牛奶的混帐老子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工地打电话来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你们一个也没去上工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你们不用去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四个人全都被炒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伞是朋友给的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.91,0:13:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的朋友真好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了  有AK二字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了租这房子把钱都花光了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我会再存的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天和这个一起睡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.38,0:13:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会梦见下雨的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想快点下雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.71,0:13:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午在书店消磨时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到一个极漂亮的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（哈？关我什么事）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫樱丘圣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.01,0:14:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她定了本叫什么迷宫的书
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.71,0:14:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前只看过参考书和名作全集之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么样的书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野君  你看过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不看  不是很感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤君不知在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没有叫你放弃摩托车
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正说了也白说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.05,0:14:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚你又上哪儿鬼混了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你到几点也不见买牛奶来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打你多少次手机也不通
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.75,0:14:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么把手机关了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是出服务区了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:15:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  肯定又是和春哉他们泡妞去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的手机也全关了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不干那些事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么关手机？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了  你没听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少来这套
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才少来这套
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是...我只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一晚上都...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.42,0:15:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和野女人寻欢作乐是吧  啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.25,0:15:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤君还是太辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（这个女人早上不是还在问我的意见吗）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤君他努力地让每一个人都活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是加藤说到底  也没啥本事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才不是没本事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.25,0:15:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信什么事都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.38,0:15:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该分工合作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:15:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:16:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野君干掉敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而加藤君专心保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.08,0:16:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得...两者都很帅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤君对所有人的生命一视同仁地珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又善良又强悍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没见过那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没见过那样的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我算是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.81,0:16:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我算是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我算是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊  只不过一晚上打不通手机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得絮叨那么久吗啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你没鬼混的话  就拿证据出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.95,0:16:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在  我在那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿个玩具枪晃啊晃  就硬起来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,象白痴一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你他妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:16:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了你！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种就来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:16:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照这儿开  来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这日子还怎么过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在经济这么不景气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上哪儿再找肯用你们的工地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的话就说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能把话讲清吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么要拖泥带水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.48,0:17:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没别的意思...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招呼也不打一声就跑来我家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又什么也不让我干
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤君、加藤君、加藤君！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.78,0:17:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  玄野君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤  加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那么回事吧  你昨晚不是问了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.91,0:17:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤他是不是一个人住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的话又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你不想跟我住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想跟那家伙住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没说过那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不说有区别么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是在利用我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再玩弄我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚出去  马上给我滚！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是供你白吃白住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个大好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再努力学习也是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人情世故  我一点不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你做饭的心意也是没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.01,0:18:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（惨了  说过了怎么办？）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野君说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上怎么会有那么美好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（慢着）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我希望你明白一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得玄野君好帅  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.01,0:18:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（说什么？）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然跟对加藤君的感觉完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:18:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（不好了  该怎么办呢）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人不是见过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就是那个“奶爸老大”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不会是幽灵吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.22,0:19:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的爸爸真混啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子白痴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是玩具枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被打傻了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  那就再杀一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我  我到底算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我  GANTZ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我们的脑袋...都被装了炸弹之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GANTZ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子怎么了  不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  站起来呀混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见没  我的奶头出奶了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你赶快回家  阿铁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经用不着我了  是吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我要离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你一直的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.52,0:20:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我希望你明白一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得玄野君好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:21:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然跟对加藤君的感觉完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.71,0:21:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.45,0:21:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都如同纯洁无暇的婴儿一般
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.18,0:21:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便遭遇困苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不要放弃，勇敢向前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便在雨中我的心因往事而作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤寂的我犹如一块浮冰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲吻我纤弱的手指吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.98,0:21:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这使我记起你的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:22:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便现在一切都结束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.81,0:22:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的那个吻我永不会忘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.88,0:22:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永不忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.28,0:22:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的吻，永不会忘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.71,0:22:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GANTZ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.91,0:22:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧闭的窗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧闭的门
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.11,0:22:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京塔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.18,0:22:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形形色色的人
